{"tid":881771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"房協：未補價資助房屋出租計劃暫未接獲租戶申請　","createTime":"2018-10-29T16:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T17:10:01.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ca5df4b7d1a16771909c77667838a2f18b18fda2","tid":881771,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:38:29.000Z","msg":"房協推出的「未補價資助出售房屋出租計劃」，至今共收到8個業主申請，其中一個因業權年期不足10年而被拒。房協已向其中一位申請人發出「合資格出租證明書」，其餘的則處理當中。計劃今日起接受租戶申請，房協暫時未收到租戶的申請。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員柯創盛表示，申請反應冷淡，是意料之內，因為業主與租客共住會產生磨擦。他又批評，申請計劃的租戶資格太嚴緊，不利於釋放過渡性房屋給有需要市民。他期望，當局將來會交由社福機構做中介人進行分租安排，確保業主能夠收到租金，租客亦能得到適切的社區支援，優化計劃。"},{"pid":"dc1db953ef4f64f424a4a7737ccbade7c43813d0","tid":881771,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:55:35.000Z","msg":"房協已經勁抵<br />\n買黎為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d1c1747e524e0eb63c0b4f2be463346db77bcf","tid":881771,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc1db953ef4f64f424a4a7737ccbade7c43813d0","tid":881771,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:55:35.000Z","msg":"房協已經勁抵<br />\n買黎為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:56:47.000Z","msg":"原來講出租自己個單位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c524ab1f7f160d496b55b131cf7d60429ae2d4e","tid":881771,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e7d1c1747e524e0eb63c0b4f2be463346db77bcf","tid":881771,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc1db953ef4f64f424a4a7737ccbade7c43813d0","tid":881771,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:55:35.000Z","msg":"房協已經勁抵<br />\n買黎為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:56:47.000Z","msg":"原來講出租自己個單位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3